ğŸ–¥ï¸ Essential Commands & Insights
Managing Processes:

Pause a process: Ctrl + Z
Resume a paused process: fg [job ID]
View running jobs: jobs
Monitoring System Resources:

Analyze CPU and RAM usage with ps -aux.
Identify specific process IDs using pgrep [process name].
Terminate processes gracefully or forcefully with kill -9 [PID].
